# Constructors, `this`, and overloading

## Multiple constructors

- Same name, different parameter lists
- One can **delegate** to another with `this(...)`

```java
public Rectangle(int w, int h) { ... }
public Rectangle(int side) { this(side, side); }  // square
```

## Overloading

- Same **method** name, different parameter list
- Compiler picks at the call site — **compile-time** only
